  "text": "<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \".github/workflows/deploy-staging.yml\",\n    \"content\": \"name: Deploy to Staging\\n\\non:\\n  push:\\n    branches:\\n      - main\\n\\njobs:\\n  deploy:\\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\\n\\n    steps:\\n      - name: Checkout code\\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\\n\\n      - name: Set up Node.js\\n        uses: actions/setup-node@v4\\n        with:\\n          node-version: '20'\\n          cache: 'npm'\\n\\n      - name: Install dependencies\\n        run: npm ci # Use npm ci for consistent, faster, and safer installs\\n\\n      - name: Build project\\n        run: npm run build\\n\\n      - name: Deploy to Staging\\n        # Example deployment script\\n        run: echo \\\"Deploying to staging environment...\\\"\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n<review_request>\n{\n  \"title\": \"Staging 배포 파이프라인 안정성 강화 (npm ci 적용)\",\n  \"assignee\": \"dev_advisor\",\n  \"message\": \"Staging 배포 워크플로우(`deploy-staging.yml`)의 의존성 설치 명령어를 `npm install`에서 `npm ci`로 변경하여 빌드 재현성과 안정성을 확보했습니다. 변경 사항에 대한 코드 리뷰 및 승인 부탁드립니다.\"\n}\n</review_request>",
